title: Small help, not asking for money
selftext: Hello guys, I have been trading for 6 months and lost 90% of fathers money and through these 2 years I have learnt a lot, but now I don't have any funds, so below I'm posting a link to join a discord server, if I win I will get a challenge account and will help a lot, plz guys join the server plz plz 🙏🥺🙏🙏
